{"tid":445432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"欅坂46交流區第三十九回:小林由依18歲生日快樂🎉","createTime":"2017-10-23T11:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T17:31:59.000Z","uid":191,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"13f0d05d8b4f1ae3ce0027bf1a8e0c14a1363ecd","tid":445432,"uid":191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:27:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小林さんお誕生日おめでとう!!</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s3fiXgL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs3fiXgL.gif&h=d64e4a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kIW7mlj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkIW7mlj.gif&h=95dc42fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jX7n78H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjX7n78H.gif&h=703830aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xvQJaUW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxvQJaUW.gif&h=f3eb09e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/020230_b9331b514fb885b933e889c2825caf75.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F020230_b9331b514fb885b933e889c2825caf75.gif&h=e7566900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46(Keyakizaka46)是日本大型女子偶像組合乃木坂46的姐妹組合</span>，製作人同樣為秋元康。組合名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。2016年4月6日，欅坂46出道單曲《サイレントマジョリティー》販售，首週銷量達261,580枚，除了登上Oricon週榜首位，還同時刷新歷代女性藝人銷量最高的出道單曲。同年5月8日，在SHOWROOM公布平假名欅坂46的合格成員。2016年12月31日，首次登場NHK紅白歌合戰。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.keyakizaka46.com/img/14/diar/88/mem/member/sub-member-6897_jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimg%2F14%2Fdiar%2F88%2Fmem%2Fmember%2Fsub-member-6897_jpg.jpg&h=c3ef22e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成員名單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n欅坂46<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/bK1naOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FbK1naOV.jpg&h=d95d6bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nけやき坂46 (ひらがなけやき)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/gglDffE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgglDffE.jpg&h=8c67622d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/014743_335e53af72e710eeffa2720180384abb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F014743_335e53af72e710eeffa2720180384abb.jpg&h=1c8fd2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5thシングル『風に吹かれても』2017.10.25 発売</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/015108_aed472fe8ec92b7bc36c5dbb674c033c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F015108_aed472fe8ec92b7bc36c5dbb674c033c.jpg&h=bba9a88f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">けやき坂46主演連続ドラマ「Re:Mind」2017年10月19日より毎週木曜午前0:59〜（水曜深夜）日本テレビにて放送スタート！</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【成員有幾靚女？】我直接用例子答你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/015803_de20d1ae6a2535222edb61a83bd10004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F015803_de20d1ae6a2535222edb61a83bd10004.jpg&h=975810f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/015803_07ed070796bc0dc89f5990a754e8533e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F015803_07ed070796bc0dc89f5990a754e8533e.jpg&h=6771ff30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/015803_865edfc5cc575ee577d69b32841f2cf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F015803_865edfc5cc575ee577d69b32841f2cf1.jpg&h=4463b26e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fkeyakizaka46sort.html&d=HVOq8Qeh7io7gLjXbC4SRDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5cb81dfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1）欅坂46乃何許人也？ <br />\n簡單來說，欅坂46是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。 <br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買欅坂46既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？ <br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP/會場購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。 <br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論坂道以外的組合？ <br />\n不可。皆因這裡主要討論欅坂46，你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員(禾ru除外)，但請先作好世界大戰的準備。 <br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到欅坂46成員？ <br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，不要幻想他們來港舉辦握手會，因為此舉極為傻豬。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n5) 呢度大佬係? <br />\n沒有<br />\n<br />\n6）會員舞木香純是咪HIHI？<br />\n是。因為三槍為人臭串、極度無恥，自然會引起其他手足責罵他。雖然佢犯禁逼走不少手足，但因他臉皮極厚，罵極不走真是無可奈何。 <br />\n<br />\n7）除了坂道46系，有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DMjuCw_V4AAURbF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDMjuCw_V4AAURbF.jpg&h=9aa524e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DMympxyUMAEaMuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDMympxyUMAEaMuq.jpg&h=8b9b76a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=HVOq8Qeh7io7gLjXbC4SRDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2d08626b\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"0ad2dae5ce69fb85f6999c1b576059967a1fbaad","tid":445432,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f3fddfbaa50536e87e7800f200e0aa5e1fd93ff1","tid":445432,"uid":94619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🎉</span>小林由依生日快樂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🎉</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/193507_ca24620319fcbd2dee21acde3a68978f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F193507_ca24620319fcbd2dee21acde3a68978f.jpg&h=98c997a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b37089a79195ee219e5de72536ec55388213af9","tid":445432,"uid":34333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"玩欅のキセキ岩岩入坑既新人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bd34779fd8fd844ca4947f